RE I just recently paid for a portion of our AtT bill with the rest of the free money in our Waterhouse account wrote a check in the amount of like The remaining balance is something like All of that amount is allocated to our monthly savings for propertyschool taxes I guess what youre saying is you would like to borrow from this savings account to make this investment As long as you feel confident that we will be able to reimburse that amount somehow to pay our taxes should we not get a return on the investment then I guess we should go for it if its something youre excited about and believe is a good investment Naturally I would prefer we only invest because of the risk involved and Christmas just around the corner but youre the one with the financial instincts and knowhow Wifey Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday October AM To Subject Hey how much of the money in our Waterhouse account is budgeted for expenses I am thinking that it would be a good investment speculative in nature though to purchase some options on Enron The options would expire in January and the potential return could vary between a loss of of the investment to a return I think between a investment would be wise given the nature of it MC

FW Wedding photosYo Sweets thought you might want to see these I also just replied and gave her your email address but you may want to contact her directly yourself Tu Esposa Original Message From Stephanie Owens mailto Sent Sunday October PM To Subject Wedding photos Hey Zo So you got a new job I didnt know Congratulations I guess you are just getting adjusted Well Im about to have to get readjusted when I go back to work in a week or so Im ready though Martin said you had a good time on your honeymoon aside from the big bruise on your ass I did the same thing in New Braunfels several years ago It looked worse than it felt Oh could you give me Martins email address at work Kevin keeps meaning to get back with him about his fathers employment situation Ill make sure he does that tomorrow Im sending some wedding photos Ill have to send only a few at a time so you will see other messages from me Let me know if you want to have any of them printed up Steph hereshecomesjpg zowalkingjpg takingvowsjpg closeupvowsjpg closeupvowsjpg almostoverjpg mrandmrsjpg

RE StarI hope you didnt tell Star that we cancelled the purchase though because if so seems like we lose our bargainng leverage to get them to come down off the floor price Then again at some point I guess I should stop worrying about trying to save the moolah and just be happy about having the pretty furniture in our home Still sure would be nice if you could work your trading magic to get us some kind of discount off the floor price Whatcha wanna do on the choice of bed situation L The Wif Original Message From Cuilla Martin mailtoMartin NRONcom Sent Thursday October PM To Subject Star I sent an email to the prez of Star about the furniture and cancelled our purchase from Furniture USA The said we should get a cedit on our credit card in days Hopefully I will hear from him soon and we will have spankin new furniture This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you

RE carSweets can you please call Wil Eanes at Allstate when you get some free time and ask him how we can make sure the Lexus will be covered next week when we go to pick it up on the th What information does he need from us Can you get it from Chris and give to him as I would prefer to have the car covered before I start driving it around Luv The Wif Original Message From Cuilla Martin mailtoMartin NRONcom Sent Thursday September PM To Subject car I talked to both Carmax and Honda and basically all we need to do is go in before pm so Carmax can talk to Honda and bring your info for the loan They call Honda and get a payoff which is and then cut us a check for the difference We should probably do that about pm on the th then we can go pick up theL exus from Dorland This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you

RE Small WorldI thought you had seen an engagement ring on Danas finger and asked her about it one time but she was vague on when exactly Hmmm I wonder where they are planning on doing it Original Message From Cuilla Martin mailtoMartin NRONcom Sent Monday October AM To Subject FW Small World I got this email from a guy I talk to occationally in Canada I didnt know they were getting married Original Message From Campbell Scott Sent Monday October AM To Cuilla Martin Subject Small World Martin Apparently you live right next door to friends of mine Dana Welsh and Gerald King were neighbors of mine when I lived in Houston in and my wife and I still keep in contact with them As a matter of fact well be staying with them on November before their wedding and might knock on your door to meet you Funny Dana mentioned in the past you worked for Enron but its such a big company I didnt think I might know you Regards T Scott Campbell Director Enron Energy Services Canada Corp th Floor th Avenue SW Calgary AB TP G phone fax This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
